{"tid":809330,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓巿核爆】日出康城3房827萬沽　三個月劈價1球","createTime":"2018-09-07T05:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T11:45:39.000Z","uid":163207,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"39120fc454c4d6fd294f827dac58754e9dd67cf6","tid":809330,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180906/58652323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180906%2F58652323&d=8cj%2FbY%2FAzXB5OU3FbZS5mNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=39cc4696\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180906%2F58652323&h=8cab90dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180906/58652323</a><br />\n <br />\n日出康城領峯3房827萬沽，3個月劈價1球。<br />\n<br />\n日出康城大型新盤LP6即將開售，加上近日環球經濟不明朗，區內二手現劈價成交。<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業林志堅表示，日出康城領峯7座右翼低層D室，實用面積673方呎，建築面積約901方呎，屬3房1套間隔。據悉，單位原於6月份以920萬元放盤，惟外圍經濟轉淡，加上8月份康城二手交投量偏低，遂接受現實決定降價，並以827萬元易手，減價93萬元，減幅約1成，呎價12,288元，建築呎價約9,179元。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，雖然業主是次減價1成求售，但其於2015年7月斥資約646萬元購入，是次轉手帳面仍獲利181萬元，升值28%。<br />\n<br />\n本報於本港三家銀行作網上估價，其中最保守為中銀，該單位估值約851萬元，是次成交較估值低24萬元或2.8%。最進取為恒生銀行估值876萬元，即成交低估值達49萬元或5.6%。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afcf8ff936c1743a64fb1069d237ea36e565616","tid":809330,"uid":163207,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:50:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">顫抖吧AA!!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7e7ef888a8452b93086727dc0878685aaa010e7c","tid":809330,"uid":100638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"短炒唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf678bd5d513